12
00:00:26,880 --> 00:00:28,199
Stay away from him.

13
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:31,957
Look, I'm sorry, that movie sucked.

14
00:00:32,120 --> 00:00:34,190
- <i>Master of the Flying Guillotine?</i>
- Yes.

15
00:00:34,360 --> 00:00:37,591
It's a classic of the genre. It's the
<i>Madame Bovary</i> of martial-art cinema.

16
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:40,433
The flying guillotine, was that
the spiky hat thing he threw?

17
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:43,034
- I'm sorry, but that was kind of weak.
<i>- Et tu,</i> Ryan?

18
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:46,670
It didn't make sense. Why was he going
after the one-armed boxer? Poor guy.

19
00:00:46,840 --> 00:00:48,239
Revenge. A tale as old as time.

20
00:00:48,400 --> 00:00:51,437
- Maybe the girls should pick next time.
- Yes.

21
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:53,875
Do I have to remind you
about the <i>Bring It On</i> phase?

22
00:00:54,040 --> 00:00:55,951
