27
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:04,910
<i>- I'm wanted, I'm hot, l...</i>
- Summer.

28
00:01:05,960 --> 00:01:07,279
Man, what'd I say?

29
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:11,592
Ten-to-one our boys are hanging out
at that candy-ass diner on the pier.

30
00:01:12,240 --> 00:01:13,992
That's what I love about you rich kids.

31
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:16,310
- So predictable.
- What do you want?

32
00:01:16,720 --> 00:01:19,154
I gotta spell it out for you?
I want a rematch.

33
00:01:19,320 --> 00:01:21,914
Somewhere private.
Just me kicking your ass.

34
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:25,191
