Or that's unnecessary continuity.
Either, or.

39
00:01:39,520 --> 00:01:40,839
Look, guys, this is so stupid.

40
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:43,594
- I got nothing against you.
- That's too bad.

41
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:47,036
Because me and you,
we got unfinished business.

42
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:54,158
See you, guys.

43
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:31,715
Hey, baby. I need your opinion.

44
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:34,678
Which of these screams
"real-estate mogul with a heart of gold"?

45
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:36,594
The blue.

46
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:42,153
