of talent and mystery."

47
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:45,279
- The blue.
- All right, blue it is.

48
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:48,034
Sandy, you're gonna do great.

49
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,918
The Newport Group's lucky
to have you.

50
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:52,555
I just wanna make a good impression
on my first day.

51
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:54,472
Hey, how's that charity thing coming?

52
00:02:54,640 --> 00:02:57,996
Oh, it's coming. I've just never thrown
together something so quickly.

53
00:02:58,160 --> 00:03:01,596
