getting Mystics while you do the work.

54
00:03:01,760 --> 00:03:04,320
Don't worry, they're working.
Busy with the foundation.

55
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:06,311
Oh, good question.

56
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:09,153
- Booze or no booze?
- Oh, tough call.

57
00:03:09,320 --> 00:03:12,357
