a couple of shots under their belt.

61
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,474
- Booze.
- Booze.

62
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:23,391
- Morning.
- Oh, hey, boys.

63
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:26,279
