some help with the party.

64
00:03:26,440 --> 00:03:28,112
Sunday. Sunday.

65
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,918
Yeah, it's gonna be tough.

66
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:32,510
- Yeah, no problem.
- Thanks, Ryan.

67
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:36,389
Well, I should get going. I have to meet
Charlotte and Julie at the club.

68
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:42,431
Hey, what is so incredibly
pressing on a Sunday?

69
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:45,030
